ly period (average ~3325ms).\n  \n2. **Checkout Service Delays:**\n   - Requests from `frontend-0` to `checkoutservice-0` showed delay reductions, but this might indicate inconsistent latency issues.\n   - Normal avg duration: ~152118ms, reduced to ~64790ms during anomalies, showing overhead handling.\n\n3. **Significant Delays in Cart Service:**\n   - From `checkoutservice-0` to `cartservice-0` for `EmptyCart` operation and others, showing ~7x increase from ~2569ms to ~18247ms.\n   - Anomalies twice noted.\n\n4. **Redis Backend Performance Issues:**\n   - `cartservice-2` facing delays with `HGET`, revealing ~14515ms average duration against ~1553ms, notably high.\n   \n5. **Express Product Catalog Service Queries:**\n   - Calls to `productcatalogservice-0` showing variance, though not prominent.\n   \n6. **Intermittent Service Communication:**\n   - Transition times increased for `emailservice-1` and `shippingservice-1`, though less consistent on frequency.\n\n7. **Minor variations across Frontend requests:**\n   - `frontend-1` performance on `\"CurrencyService/Convert\"` indicates increased average during anomalies.\n\n### Detected Trace Keys:\n- `latency_spike`\n- `checkoutservice->cartservice`\n- `cartservice->redis`\n- `frontend->recommendationservice`\n\n### Hypotheses\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"frontend->recommendationservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant delay and high variance in `EmptyCart` and `GetCart` operations.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Increased duration from ~2569ms to ~18247ms, suggesting potential bottleneck or resource issues.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"Backend slow response affecting `cartservice` operations.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Prolonged response time for HGET operation, averaging ~14515ms from ~1553ms.\